rComments: Nice person but TERRIBLE PROF! Avoid if possible! Cancels tons of classes, is unable to answer questions in class, and conveys the subject matter in a very confusing way. She uses the old version of the text which has slightly different cases and emphases making class very confusing. Shes relatively easy, finished class with a B+ with little effort

Small group. Straight lecture style. Not very helpful syllabus. Focuses on cases in textbook notes as well. Talks relatively fast which is a problem if you don't know which case she's referring to. Heavy readings although Torts is not as complicated as Contracts. Straightforward exams but she curved down as a result. Fair marker. Easy-going.
